INTRODUCTION

PTE Practice ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you use our mobile application PTE Practice (the "App").

By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

INFORMATION WE COLLECT

We collect the following types of information:

1. Practice Data
   - Test scores and performance metrics
   - Question response history
   - Weak area identification data
   - This data is stored locally on your device

2. App Usage Information
   - Features used within the App
   - Session duration
   - This data is used for analytics purposes

HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION

We use the collected information to:

1. Provide and maintain the App's functionality
2. Track your learning progress and performance
3. Identify areas where you need improvement
4. Improve the App's user experience
5. Generate analytics and statistics about your practice sessions

DATA STORAGE AND SECURITY

1. Local Storage: All practice data and test results are stored locally on your device using secure storage mechanisms.

2. No Cloud Storage: We do not currently store your practice data on external servers.

3. Security: We implement appropriate security measures to protect the information stored on your device.

DATA SHARING

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. We may share aggregated, non-personally identifiable information for research or improvement purposes.

CHILDREN'S PRIVACY

The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.

